{
  "video_id": "zamvnyBB-SU",
  "title": "Why the hospital of the future will be your own home | Niels van Namen",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13600.0,
      "end_time": 16175.0,
      "text": "Probably not a surprise to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16200.0,
      "end_time": 18336.0,
      "text": "but I don&#39;t like to be in a hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18360.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "or go to a hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20390.0,
      "end_time": 21816.0,
      "text": "Do you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21840.0,
      "end_time": 24296.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure many of you feel the same way, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24320.0,
      "end_time": 28335.0,
      "text": "But why? Why is it that we hate hospitals so much?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28360.0,
      "end_time": 30720.0,
      "text": "Or is it just a fact of life we have to live with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31680.0,
      "end_time": 33440.0,
      "text": "Is it the crappy food?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34480.0,
      "end_time": 36535.0,
      "text": "Is it the expensive parking?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36560.0,
      "end_time": 38336.0,
      "text": "Is it the intense smell?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38360.0,
      "end_time": 40240.0,
      "text": "Or is it the fear of the unknown?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41400.0,
      "end_time": 44400.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s all of that, and it&#39;s more."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45160.0,
      "end_time": 47656.0,
      "text": "Patients often have to travel long distances"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47680.0,
      "end_time": 49280.0,
      "text": "to get to their nearest hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50920.0,
      "end_time": 54256.0,
      "text": "and access to hospital care is becoming more and more an issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54280.0,
      "end_time": 55936.0,
      "text": "in rural areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55960.0,
      "end_time": 57256.0,
      "text": "in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57280.0,
      "end_time": 60800.0,
      "text": "but also in sparsely populated countries like Sweden."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61240.0,
      "end_time": 64120.0,
      "text": "And even when hospitals are more abundant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65400.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67560.0,
      "text": "typically the poor and the elderly"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67800.0,
      "end_time": 70136.0,
      "text": "have trouble getting care because they lack transportation"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70160.0,
      "end_time": 72600.0,
      "text": "that is convenient and affordable to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73840.0,
      "end_time": 78376.0,
      "text": "And many people are avoiding hospital care altogether,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78400.0,
      "end_time": 80416.0,
      "text": "and they miss getting proper treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80440.0,
      "end_time": 81640.0,
      "text": "due to cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82720.0,
      "end_time": 86416.0,
      "text": "We see that 64 percent of Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 89000.0,
      "text": "are avoiding care due to cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90760.0,
      "end_time": 93816.0,
      "text": "And even when you do get treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93840.0,
      "end_time": 95920.0,
      "text": "hospitals often make us sicker."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97320.0,
      "end_time": 102800.0,
      "text": "Medical errors are reported to be the third cause of death in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103120.0,
      "end_time": 106536.0,
      "text": "just behind cancer and heart disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106560.0,
      "end_time": 108400.0,
      "text": "the third cause of death."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109680.0,
      "end_time": 111776.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m in health care for over 20 years now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111800.0,
      "end_time": 117479.0,
      "text": "and I witness every day how broken and how obsolete our hospital system is."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118440.0,
      "end_time": 120176.0,
      "text": "Let me give you two examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120200.0,
      "end_time": 123456.0,
      "text": "Four in 10 Japanese medical doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123480.0,
      "end_time": 126296.0,
      "text": "and five in 10 American medical doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 126320.0,
      "end_time": 127520.0,
      "text": "are burnt out."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128520.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130976.00000000001,
      "text": "In my home country, the Netherlands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131000.0,
      "end_time": 133176.0,
      "text": "only 17 million people live there."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133200.0,
      "end_time": 137959.0,
      "text": "We are short 125,000 nurses over the coming years."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139920.0,
      "end_time": 141655.0,
      "text": "But how did we even end up here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141680.0,
      "end_time": 144496.0,
      "text": "in this idea of placing all kinds of sick people"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144520.0,
      "end_time": 146200.0,
      "text": "together in one big building?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147680.0,
      "end_time": 150400.0,
      "text": "Well, we have to go back to the Ancient Greeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 151200.0,
      "end_time": 154335.0,
      "text": "In 400 BC, temples for cure were erected"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154360.0,
      "end_time": 156856.0,
      "text": "where people could go to get their diagnosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156880.0,
      "end_time": 159335.0,
      "text": "their treatment and their healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159360.0,
      "end_time": 162776.0,
      "text": "And then really for about 2,000 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162800.0,
      "end_time": 165296.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve seen religious care centers"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165320.0,
      "end_time": 168896.0,
      "text": "all the way up to the Industrial Revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168920.0,
      "end_time": 174790.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;ve seen hospitals being set up as assembly lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176000.0,
      "end_time": 178496.0,
      "text": "based on the principles of the Industrial Revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 178520.0,
      "end_time": 179976.0,
      "text": "to produce efficiently"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180000.0,
      "end_time": 182736.0,
      "text": "and get the products, the patients in this case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182760.0,
      "end_time": 185120.0,
      "text": "out of the hospital as soon as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186520.0,
      "end_time": 190816.0,
      "text": "Over the last century, we&#39;ve seen lots of interesting innovations."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190840.0,
      "end_time": 193296.0,
      "text": "We figured out how to make insulin."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193320.0,
      "end_time": 196960.0,
      "text": "We invented pacemakers and X-ray,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196120.0,
      "end_time": 200720.0,
      "text": "and we even came into this wonderful new era of cell and gene therapies."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201800.0,
      "end_time": 206296.0,
      "text": "But the biggest change to fix our hospital system altogether"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206320.0,
      "end_time": 208335.0,
      "text": "is still ahead of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208360.0,
      "end_time": 211216.0,
      "text": "And I believe it&#39;s time now, we have the opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211240.0,
      "end_time": 214296.0,
      "text": "to revolutionize the system altogether"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214320.0,
      "end_time": 217960.0,
      "text": "and forget about our current hospital system."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 217120.0,
      "end_time": 219336.0,
      "text": "I believe it&#39;s time to create a new system"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219360.0,
      "end_time": 221920.0,
      "text": "that revolves around health care at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 223840.0,
      "end_time": 226416.0,
      "text": "Recent research has shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226440.0,
      "end_time": 229696.0,
      "text": "that 46 percent of hospital care"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 229720.0,
      "end_time": 231240.0,
      "text": "can move to the patient&#39;s home."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232400.0,
      "end_time": 234176.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234200.0,
      "end_time": 238536.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s mainly for those patients who suffer from chronic diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238560.0,
      "end_time": 241536.0,
      "text": "With that, hospitals can and should"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241560.0,
      "end_time": 245496.0,
      "text": "reduce to smaller, agile and mobile care centers"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245520.0,
      "end_time": 246800.0,
      "text": "focused on acute care."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247840.0,
      "end_time": 253936.0,
      "text": "So things like neonatology, intensive care, surgery and imaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253960.0,
      "end_time": 256160.0,
      "text": "will still remain at the hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 256399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 258799.99999999997,
      "text": "at least I believe for the foreseeable future."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262576.0,
      "text": "A few weeks ago, I met a colleague"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 262600.0,
      "end_time": 265856.0,
      "text": "whose mom was diagnosed with incurable cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 265880.0,
      "end_time": 267695.0,
      "text": "and she said, \"Niels, it&#39;s hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267720.0,
      "end_time": 271480.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so hard when we know that she&#39;s got only months to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 272560.0,
      "end_time": 274616.0,
      "text": "Instead of playing with the grandchildren,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 274640.0,
      "end_time": 278135.0,
      "text": "she now has to travel three times a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 278160.0,
      "end_time": 280136.0,
      "text": "two hours up and down to Amsterdam"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 280160.0,
      "end_time": 282800.0,
      "text": "just to get her treatment and tests.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283160.0,
      "end_time": 285576.0,
      "text": "And that really breaks my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 285600.0,
      "end_time": 289960.0,
      "text": "because we all know that a professional nurse"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 289120.0,
      "end_time": 291696.0,
      "text": "could draw her blood at home as well, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 291720.0,
      "end_time": 295336.0,
      "text": "And if she could get her tests and treatment at home as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 295360.0,
      "end_time": 298736.0,
      "text": "she could do the things that are really important to her"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 298760.0,
      "end_time": 300360.0,
      "text": "in her last months."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301160.0,
      "end_time": 304920.0,
      "text": "My own mom, 82 years old now -- God bless her --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 306720.0,
      "end_time": 308576.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s avoiding to go to the hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308600.0,
      "end_time": 312536.0,
      "text": "because she finds it difficult to plan and manage the journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 312560.0,
      "end_time": 315536.0,
      "text": "So my sisters and I, we help her out."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 315560.0,
      "end_time": 318776.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s many elderly people who are avoiding care"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 318800.0,
      "end_time": 322216.0,
      "text": "and are waiting that long that it becomes life-threatening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 322240.0,
      "end_time": 324920.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s straight to the costly, intensive care."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 326240.0,
      "end_time": 330960.0,
      "text": "Dr. Covinsky, a clinical researcher at the University of California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 330120.0,
      "end_time": 333656.0,
      "text": "he concludes that a third of patients over 70"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 333680.0,
      "end_time": 336776.0,
      "text": "and more than half of patients over 85,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 336800.0,
      "end_time": 339840.0,
      "text": "leave the hospital more disabled than when they came in."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 341360.0,
      "end_time": 344896.0,
      "text": "And a very practical problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 344920.0,
      "end_time": 348376.0,
      "text": "that many patients face when they have to go to a hospital is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 348400.0,
      "end_time": 352936.0,
      "text": "Where do I go with my main companion in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 352960.0,
      "end_time": 354599.0,
      "text": "where do I go with my dog?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 357240.0,
      "end_time": 359296.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s our dog, by the way. Isn&#39;t she cute?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 359320.0,
      "end_time": 361960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 362880.0,
      "end_time": 364856.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not only about convenience."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 364880.0,
      "end_time": 369000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also about unnecessary health care stays and costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 369800.0,
      "end_time": 371256.0,
      "text": "A friend of mine, Art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371280.0,
      "end_time": 375950.0,
      "text": "he recently needed to be hospitalized for just a minor surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 375120.0,
      "end_time": 377856.0,
      "text": "and he had to stay in the hospital for over two weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377880.0,
      "end_time": 381816.0,
      "text": "just because he needed a specific kind of IV antibiotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 381840.0,
      "end_time": 385150.0,
      "text": "So he occupied a bed for two weeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 385400.0,
      "end_time": 387816.0,
      "text": "that cost over a thousand euros a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 387840.0,
      "end_time": 389816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just ridiculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 389840.0,
      "end_time": 392856.0,
      "text": "And these costs are really at the heart of the issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 392880.0,
      "end_time": 395135.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve seen over many of our global economies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 395160.0,
      "end_time": 398336.0,
      "text": "health care expense grow as a percentage of GDP"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 398360.0,
      "end_time": 400560.0,
      "text": "over the last years."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 400800.0,
      "end_time": 403150.0,
      "text": "So here we see that over the last 50 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 403400.0,
      "end_time": 407560.0,
      "text": "health care expense has grown from about five percent in Germany"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 407800.0,
      "end_time": 408919.0,
      "text": "to about 11 percent now."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 410000.0,
      "end_time": 414960.0,
      "text": "In the US, we&#39;ve seen growth from six percent to over 17 percent now."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 416160.0,
      "end_time": 420136.0,
      "text": "And a large portion of these costs are driven by investments"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 420160.0,
      "end_time": 422920.0,
      "text": "in large, shiny hospital buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 423720.0,
      "end_time": 425536.0,
      "text": "And these buildings are not flexible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 425560.0,
      "end_time": 428696.0,
      "text": "and they maintain a system where hospital beds need to be filled"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 428720.0,
      "end_time": 430360.0,
      "text": "for a hospital to run efficiently."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 431480.0,
      "end_time": 434680.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no incentive for a hospital to run with less beds."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 435880.0,
      "end_time": 438800.0,
      "text": "Just the thought of that makes you sick, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 438960.0,
      "end_time": 442695.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s the thing: the cost for treating my buddy Art at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 442720.0,
      "end_time": 445960.0,
      "text": "can be up to 10 times cheaper than hospital care."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 447240.0,
      "end_time": 448720.0,
      "text": "And that is where we&#39;re headed."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 452840.0,
      "text": "The hospital bed of the future will be in our own homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 454240.0,
      "end_time": 455576.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s already starting."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 455600.0,
      "end_time": 459616.0,
      "text": "Global home care is growing 10 percent year over year."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 459640.0,
      "end_time": 464216.0,
      "text": "And from my own experience, I see that logistics and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 464240.0,
      "end_time": 466720.0,
      "text": "are making these home health care solutions work."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 468240.0,
      "end_time": 470536.0,
      "text": "Technology is already allowing us to do things"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 470560.0,
      "end_time": 472600.0,
      "text": "that were once exclusive to hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 473720.0,
      "end_time": 475400.0,
      "text": "Diagnosis tests like blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 476400.0,
      "end_time": 481560.0,
      "text": "glucose tests, urine tests, can now be taken in the comfort of our homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 481800.0,
      "end_time": 483800.0,
      "text": "And more and more connected devices"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 485400.0,
      "end_time": 488960.0,
      "text": "we see like pacemakers and insulin pumps"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 488120.0,
      "end_time": 491760.0,
      "text": "that will proactively signal if help is needed soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 492840.0,
      "end_time": 494895.0,
      "text": "And all that technology is coming together"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 494920.0,
      "end_time": 498216.0,
      "text": "in much more insights into the patients&#39; health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 498240.0,
      "end_time": 502256.0,
      "text": "and that insight and all of the information leads to better control"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 502280.0,
      "end_time": 504335.0,
      "text": "and to less medical errors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 504360.0,
      "end_time": 507136.0,
      "text": "remember, the third cause of death"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 507160.0,
      "end_time": 508360.0,
      "text": "in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 509600.0,
      "end_time": 511336.0,
      "text": "And I see it every day at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 511360.0,
      "end_time": 513560.0,
      "text": "I work in logistics"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 513799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 516559.99999999994,
      "text": "and for me, home health care works."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 518390.0,
      "end_time": 522175.0,
      "text": "So we see a delivery driver deliver the medicine"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 522200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523400.00000000006,
      "text": "to the patient&#39;s home."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 524480.0,
      "end_time": 527936.0,
      "text": "A nurse joins him and actually administers the drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 527960.0,
      "end_time": 529159.0,
      "text": "at the patient&#39;s home."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 530679.0,
      "end_time": 532376.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 532400.0,
      "end_time": 534150.0,
      "text": "Remember my buddy, Art?"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 534390.0,
      "end_time": 537816.0,
      "text": "He can now get the IV antibiotics in the comfort of his home:"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 537840.0,
      "end_time": 541576.0,
      "text": "no hospital pajamas, no crappy food"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 541600.0,
      "end_time": 546456.0,
      "text": "and no risk of these antibiotic-resistant superbugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 546480.0,
      "end_time": 548856.0,
      "text": "that only bite you in these hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 548880.0,
      "end_time": 550136.0,
      "text": "And it goes further."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 550160.0,
      "end_time": 554656.0,
      "text": "So now the elderly people can get the treatment that they need"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 554680.0,
      "end_time": 556656.0,
      "text": "in the comfort of their own home"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 556680.0,
      "end_time": 559175.0,
      "text": "while with their best companion in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 559200.0,
      "end_time": 562536.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s no need anymore to drive hours and hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 562560.0,
      "end_time": 564439.0,
      "text": "just to get your treatment and tests."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 565560.0,
      "end_time": 567215.0,
      "text": "In the Netherlands and in Denmark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 567240.0,
      "end_time": 569936.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve seen very good successes in cancer clinics"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 569960.0,
      "end_time": 573120.0,
      "text": "organizing chemotherapies at the patient&#39;s homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 574360.0,
      "end_time": 576680.0,
      "text": "sometimes even together with fellow patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 578800.0,
      "end_time": 580616.0,
      "text": "The best improvements for these patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 580640.0,
      "end_time": 584136.0,
      "text": "have been improvements in reduction in stress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 584160.0,
      "end_time": 586719.0,
      "text": "anxiety disorders and depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 587920.0,
      "end_time": 591575.0,
      "text": "Home health care also helped them to get back a sense of normality"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 591600.0,
      "end_time": 593936.0,
      "text": "and freedom in their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 593960.0,
      "end_time": 598000.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve actually helped them to forget about their disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 599600.0,
      "end_time": 602216.0,
      "text": "But home health care, Niels --"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 602240.0,
      "end_time": 606136.0,
      "text": "what if I don&#39;t even have a home, when I&#39;m homeless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 606160.0,
      "end_time": 609536.0,
      "text": "or when I do have a home but there&#39;s no one to take care of me"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 609560.0,
      "end_time": 611239.0,
      "text": "or even open up the door?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 612400.0,
      "end_time": 615415.0,
      "text": "Well, in comes our sharing economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 615440.0,
      "end_time": 619336.0,
      "text": "or, as I like to call it, the Airbnb for home care."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 619360.0,
      "end_time": 622696.0,
      "text": "In the Netherlands, we see churches and care organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 622720.0,
      "end_time": 625576.0,
      "text": "match people in need of care and company"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 625600.0,
      "end_time": 627736.0,
      "text": "with people who actually have a home for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 627760.0,
      "end_time": 629720.0,
      "text": "and can provide care and company to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 630520.0,
      "end_time": 632415.0,
      "text": "Home health care is cheaper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 632440.0,
      "end_time": 636560.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s easier to facilitate, and it&#39;s quick to set up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 636800.0,
      "end_time": 640656.0,
      "text": "in these rural areas we talked about, but also in humanitarian crisis situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 640680.0,
      "end_time": 646359.0,
      "text": "where it&#39;s often safer, quicker and cheaper to set things up at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 648800.0,
      "end_time": 652296.0,
      "text": "Home health care is very applicable in prosperous areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 652320.0,
      "end_time": 655896.0,
      "text": "but also very much in underserved communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 655920.0,
      "end_time": 658550.0,
      "text": "Home health care works in developed countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 658800.0,
      "end_time": 659800.0,
      "text": "as well as in developing countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 660760.0,
      "end_time": 666576.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m passionate to help facilitate improvements in patients&#39; lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 666600.0,
      "end_time": 668536.0,
      "text": "due to home health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 668560.0,
      "end_time": 670976.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m passionate to help facilitate"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 671000.0,
      "end_time": 673736.0,
      "text": "that the elderly people get the treatment that they need"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 673760.0,
      "end_time": 675496.0,
      "text": "in the comfort of their own homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 675520.0,
      "end_time": 677560.0,
      "text": "together with their best companion in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 678640.0,
      "end_time": 681136.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m passionate to make the change"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 681160.0,
      "end_time": 684736.0,
      "text": "and help ensure that patients, and not their disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 684760.0,
      "end_time": 686319.0,
      "text": "are in control of their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 687800.0,
      "end_time": 689976.0,
      "text": "To me, that is health care delivered at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 690000.0,
      "end_time": 691216.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 691240.0,
      "end_time": 695000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}